did.unittitle: Commissioner of Internal Revenue v. Howe A. Stidger, briefs

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Consists of slip opinions, issues of the Supreme Court Journal, and miscellaneous other materials printed by the Court. Also included are briefs for a Supreme Court case for which John A. Reed, Justice Reed's son, filed an amicus.
Arranged alphabetically by document type and chronologically by year.
